name: Custom Tren'di Luxe Bracelet Set
description:
To order your custom Tren'di Luxe Beaded Bracelet Set please following the steps below:

STEP 1 - Fill out the contact form under the "Contact" tab. Please put "Custom Order Request" in the subject bar.

STEP 2 - List your color scheme, the quantity of bracelets, wrist size in inches, and name (First & Last Name). Once we have received your contact form, we will email you to confirm your order.

STEP 3 - Select your bracelet set (Below The Price List) and make your payment to complete your order. Payment MUST be made within 48 hours after sending your contact form. If the payment has NOT been received within 48 hours, your order will be canceled. 

Price List:
(1) Bracelet  (Size: 6" - 7 1/2") - $13.00 + Shipping 
(2) Bracelets (Size: 6" - 7 1/2") - $24.00 + Shipping
(3) Bracelets (Size: 6" - 7 1/2") - $30.00 + Shipping
(4) Bracelets (Size: 6" - 7 1/2") - $36.00 + Shipping

Note: Additional fee of $3.00 for sizes 8" and up.

***Prices are subject to change***

description:

All of the bracelets are handmade and can be customized just for you.

(See "Custom Tren'di Luxe Bracelet Set" listing for custom orders)

name: Beaded Bracelet Watch Set #1
description:
A chunky beaded bracelet and a elegant watch face is a perfect combination. The bracelet band is made with stretchy cord and a variety of beads.

This fashionable watch set is available in a variety of colors.

Note: If you would like a white and silver watch face instead of a color watch face, please fill out the contact form under "Contact" after you have checked out your order. Please put "Watch Face Color Change" in the subject bar. In the message box, list your watch face. 

The different type of watch faces are the following:
- Silver w/ White Background (See "Pink & White" 1st Row - Right)
- Silver w/ Silver Background (See "Black Opera" 3rd Row - Right)
